\c 10
\s Akaipa anozvikudza pamberi paMwari, asi Jehovha ndiye murwiri
\p
\v 1 Munomirireiko kure, Jehovha? Munozvivanzireiko panguva dzokutambudzika?
\v 2 Pakuzvikudza kwake akaipa anotambudza murombo zvikuru; Ngavabatwe namano avakafunga.
\v 3 Nokuti wakaipa anozvirumbidza pamusoro
\s pezvinoda mwoyo wake,
\s Anoruchiva anoramba Jehovha nokumuzvidza.
\p
\v 4 Nokuzvikudza kwechiso chake, wakaipa anoti,
\s "Haangabvunzi."
\s Ndangariro dzake dzose dzinoti, "Hakuna Mwari."
\p
\v 5 Nzira dzake dzakasimba nguva dzose;
\s Zvamunotonga imi zviri kure kumusoro, haazvioni;
\s Kana vari vadzivisi vake vose, anovashora.
\p
\v 6 Anoti mumwoyo make, "Handingazununguswi;
\s Handingavi panhamo kusvikira kumarudzi angu ose."
\p
\v 7 Muromo wake uzere nokutuka nokunyengera nokumanikidza; Zvakashata nezvakaipa zviri pasi
\s porurimi rwake.
\p
\v 8 Anogara panzvimbo dzokuvanda dzemisha;
\s Pakavanda ndipo paanouraya asina mhosva;
\s Meso ake anovandira asina wokumubatsira.
\p
\v 9 Anovandira pakavanda seshumba panzvimbo yayo;
\s Anovanda kuti abate murombo; Anobata murombo, kana achimukakatira
\s mumumbure wake.
\p
\v 1 Â° Anonyangira, anokotama pasi, Vasina mubatsiri vanowiswa nesimba rake.
\p
\v 11 Anoti mumwoyo make,
\s "Mwari akanganwa;
\s Anovanza chiso chake, haangatongozvioni."
\p
\v 12 Simukai Jehovha; Mwari simudzai ruoko rwenyu;
\s Regai kukanganwa varombo.
\p
\v 13 Akaipa anozvidzireiko Mwari, Achiti mumwoyo wake, "Hangabvunzi?"
\p
\v 14 Mazviona henyu; nokuti
\s munoona kutambudzika nokuchema, kuti muzvibate muruoko rwenyu; asinamubatsiri anozviisa kwamuri; Makava mubatsiri wenherera.
\p
\v 15 Vhunai ruoko rwowakaipa.
\s Kana ari munhu akashata, nzverai zvakaipa zvake, kusvikira musingazozviwani.
\p
\v 16 Jehovha ndiye Mambo	.
\v 1 !
\s nokusingaperi-peri;
\s Vahedheni vakaparadzwa munyika yake.
\p
\v 17 Jehovha, makanzwa zvinodikanwa navanyoro;
\s Muchasimbisa mwoyo yavo, mucharerekera nzeve yenyu;
\p
\v 18 Kuti mutongere nherera
\s neanotambudzwa,
\s Kuti munhu wapanyika arege
\s kuramba achivhundusa.
